17 double Get(std::string const & nm) {
18  Local<String> getName = Nan::New<String>(nm).ToLocalChecked();
19 
20  auto rObj = inp->ToObject()->Get(getName);
21  if (rObj->IsUndefined()) {
22  ThrowTypeError(std::string("Get method in standalone.h: " + nm + " not present in object").c_str());

83 NAN_METHOD(receiverTank) {
84  inp = info[0]->ToObject();
85 
86  ReceiverTank tank;
87  ReceiverTank::Method method = static_cast<ReceiverTank::Method>(static_cast<unsigned>(Get("method")));
88 
89  if (method == ReceiverTank::Method::General) {
90  tank = {ReceiverTank::Method::General, Get("airDemand"), Get("allowablePressureDrop"), Get("atmosphericPressure")};
91  } else if (method == ReceiverTank::Method::DedicatedStorage) {
92  tank = {ReceiverTank::Method::DedicatedStorage, Get("lengthOfDemand"), Get("airFlowRequirement"), Get("atmosphericPressure"), Get("initialTankPressure"), Get("finalTankPressure")};
93  } else if (method == ReceiverTank::Method::BridgingCompressorReactionDelay) {
94  tank = {ReceiverTank::Method::BridgingCompressorReactionDelay, Get("distanceToCompressorRoom"), Get("speedOfAir"), Get("atmosphericPressure"), Get("airDemand"), Get("allowablePressureDrop")};
95  } else {
96  tank = {ReceiverTank::Method::MeteredStorage, Get("lengthOfDemand"), Get("airFlowRequirement"), Get("atmosphericPressure"), Get("initialTankPressure"), Get("finalTankPressure"), Get("meteredControl")};
97  }
98 
99  Local<Number> size = Nan::New(tank.calculateSize());
